subject: resource/Star_Soldier
object: Star Soldier (スターソルジャー, Sutā Sorujā) is a series of shoot 'em up video games mainly developed by Hudson Soft. Konami has owned the rights to the series since their absorption of Hudson Soft in 2012.The first game, named Star Soldier, appeared on the MSX and NES in 1986, and the series has continued on various gaming systems.
